item.description: Explore the Manchester Essex Woods with a local Marblehead photographer who knows all the trails well and can point out lots of interesting plants and animal tracks...we'll probably end up in his photo blog! This is a wonderful conservation area maintained by the Manchester Essex Conservation trust with board walk past a beaver pond, hilly rocky terrain and some views. I'll post the full directions later - just off 128.
